                 && !exports.isMongo

  : exports.isMongo ? 'mongo'
    : exports.isBrowser ? 'browser'

  this.name = this.constructor.name
  this.message = errorMessages[code]
  this.code = code
  if (field) this.field = field
}

util.inherits(MulterError, Error)

module.exports = MulterError
